  "body": "Reproduced on iPhone X, IOS 14.1 with connected Airpods Pro/Galaxy Buds headphones. Reproducible on release 1.19/nightly \r\nAudio messages are sent with no sound. \r\n\r\n**Steps:**\r\n1. Connect bluetooth headphones to iOS device\r\n2. Login multiaccount\r\n3. Start 1-1 chat \r\n4. Record and send an audiomessage while headphones are connected to iPhone\r\n5. Play the audio\r\n6. Pay attention if sound has been recorded\r\n\r\n**Actual result:** \r\nSound has not been recorded, silent audio messaage is sent\r\n\r\n**Expected result:**\r\nAudio has been recorded. \r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status version: release 1.19/nightly \r\n- Operating System: iOS 14.1, 15.5\r\n- Device: iPhone X, iPhone 12 mini\r\n- Headphones device: Airpods Pro/Airpods/GalaxyBuds\r\n\r\n\r\nLogs from release build is attached. \r\n[geth.log](https://github.com/status-im/status-react/files/8868418/geth.log)\r\n\r\n",
